  abstract={A meta‐analysis of eight randomized controlled trials has found an association between use of the psychostimulants modafinil or armodafinil and reduction of negative symptoms in schizophrenia, but the overall effect size was small and the outcome was no longer statistically significant when results of the only study to examine acutely ill patients were excluded.}
